            <h2 class="section-heading">HOW IT WORKS</h2>
            <p class="lead">All of your favorite television shows in one convenient place.</p>
            <p>New cable provider? DVR explode in a ball of flame during a lightning storm? Can't remember what shows you used to record? These problems can become a thing of the past with a few simple clicks.</p>
            <p>By logging into "MATT-TV" through Facebook, any and all television shows that you follow on Facebook will be added to your personal list of favorite TV shows. Access this list to see when a show premieres or when and on what station that show airs. Don't see some of your favorite shows? Head to the 'shows' page and find what you are looking for on our extensive list. A simple click of a button and you are now following that show! Never again lose track of a show. Let MATT-TV take the worry out of your free time! Get started now!</p>
            <p>
            <% if current_user %>
            <% else %>
            <a href="/users/auth/facebook"><img src="/assets/login.jpg" height="27" width="80" /></a>
            <% end %>
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <img src="assets/old_tv.jpg" class="img-responsive" alt="Image Intro">
          </div>
        </div>
